### 6-7 新規商品登録で商品名をnullで指定する
POST  http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

 {
    "name": null,
    "price": 1000,
    "description": "説明",
    "stock": 5,
    "imageUrl": "/img.png"
  }


### 6-8 新規商品登録で価格を0以下で指定する
POST  http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": 3,
    "name": "商品X",
    "price": 0,
    "description": "説明",
    "stock": 10,
    "imageUrl": "/img.png"
  }


### 6-9 新規商品登録で在庫を負数で指定する
